Single Cell analysis uses the "pyabf" library since the format of data is Axon Binary Format(ABF)

in vivo data is acquired from "intan headstages".
Reading/Making data file from rhd/rhs/rhx format files can be done by codes from https://intantech.com/downloads.html?tabSelect=Software&yPos=160

in in vivo folder, there are
1. signal_analysis.py: filtering, frequency analysis and peak selecting function is included
